_sText:
The aim of this map is to race against your team-mates and the opposing team to the castle. So first go through a swamp which slows you down then cross the bridge across the moat, but watch out for traps. Then first person to reach the top destroys everyones ropes and fall to their deaths. This FR is Footrace which is a new kind of map and are studio is currently making more.
